# type(scope): imperative summary  (≤100 chars)
#
# types:  build chore ci docs feat fix perf refactor revert style test
# scopes: overview midi-usb ble ipc platform frontend dx ci release
#         governance deps docs repo scripts spec security
#
# Body shape for non-trivial commits:
#
# Why:
# - What problem this solves.
#
# Changed:
# - What changed, grouped by surface.
#
# Spec:
# - docs/specs/XXX-name/spec.md [FR-X]
#
# Verification:
# - npm run verify
#
# Opt in with: git config commit.template .gitmessage
# @see docs/specs/400-dx-tooling/spec.md [FR-20]
